[
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "1",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084001",
        "Body":  "WHEN THE SKY is split asunder,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "10",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084010",
        "Body":  "But as for him whose record shall be given to him behind his\n\t\t\tback,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e7\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "11",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084011",
        "Body":  "he will in time pray for utter destruction:"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "12",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084012",
        "Body":  "but he will enter the blazing flame."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "13",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084013",
        "Body":  "Behold, [in his earthly life] he lived joyfully among people of\n\t\t\this own kind\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e -"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "14",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084014",
        "Body":  "for, behold, he never thought that he would have to return [to\n\t\t\tGod]."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "15",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084015",
        "Body":  "Yea indeed! His Sustainer did see all that was in him!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "16",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084016",
        "Body":  "BUT NAY! I call to witness the sunset\u0027s [fleeting] afterglow,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "17",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084017",
        "Body":  "and the night, and what it [step by step] unfolds,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "18",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084018",
        "Body":  "and the moon, as it grows to its fullness:\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e9\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "19",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084019",
        "Body":  "[even thus, O men,] are you bound to move onward from stage to\n\t\t\tstage.\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "2",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084002",
        "Body":  "obeying its Sustainer, as in truth it must;"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "20",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084020",
        "Body":  "What, then, is amiss with them that they will not believe [in a\n\t\t\tlife to come]?\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e -"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "21",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084021",
        "Body":  "and [that], when the Qur\u0027an is read unto them, they do not fall\n\t\t\tdown in prostration?\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "22",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084022",
        "Body":  "Nay, but they who are bent on denying the truth give the lie [to\n\t\t\tthis divine writ]!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "23",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084023",
        "Body":  "Yet God has full knowledge of what they conceal [in their\n\t\t\thearts].\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "24",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084024",
        "Body":  "Hence, give them the tiding of grievous suffering [in the life to\n\t\t\tcome] -"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "25",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084025",
        "Body":  "unless it be such [of them] as [repent, and] attain to faith, and\n\t\t\tdo good works: for theirs shall be a reward unending!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "3",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084003",
        "Body":  "and when the earth is levelled,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "4",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084004",
        "Body":  "and casts forth whatever is in it, and becomes utterly\n\t\t\tvoid,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "5",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084005",
        "Body":  "obeying its Sustainer, as in truth it must -:"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "6",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084006",
        "Body":  "[then,] O man - thou [that] hast, verily, been toiling towards\n\t\t\tthy Sustainer in painful toil\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e - then shalt thou meet\n\t\t\tHim!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "7",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084007",
        "Body":  "And as for him whose record shall be placed in his right\n\t\t\thand,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "8",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084008",
        "Body":  "he will in time be called to account with an easy accounting,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "84",
        "AyahNumber":  "9",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/084009",
        "Body":  "and will [be able to] turn joyfully to those of his own\n\t\t\tkind.\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e"
    }
]
